ssary to change a watchband, including tools to remove difficult watchbands or to remove or add links to a metal band. You also have tools to remove a watch battery and clean the contact points before inserting your new battery.","Some of the more complex watch tools in this kit include a watch hand remover to replace watch hands, a spring bar tool for removing pins and silicon grease to seal out moisture before replacing the back of the watch. An eye loupe provides magnification for close work. You can also use the included buff stick and siliconized cloth to clean and shine the watchcase when you are finished. This kit&#39;s tool materials are made of brass, stainless steel, wood and plastic.","Watch repair is a hobby enjoyed by many, and having the correct tools is important. Whether you&#39;re a novice or professional, the Esslinger Deluxe Tool Set offers high-quality tools that supply you with all the important basic pieces. If you are looking for a watch tool kit, this one may be worth checking out."]},"id":"3b959853-d58b-4fcc-9d22-7d2060cf0ec5","type":"text"}]],"body":null,"legacyId":"product_review_page_64063","url":"/esslinger-review","authors":[{"email":"","slug":"grant-morgan","url":"/author/grant-morgan","dateCreated":"2019-04-16T16:01:12Z","name":"Grant Morgan","dateModified":"2019-04-16T16:01:12Z","id":"5h9THR5HH34dskUikqZYj8","dateImported":null,"site":"toptenreviews"}],"territories":["US","GB"],"companies":[],"dateCreated":"2015-04-09T15:19:43Z","datePublished":"2015-04-09T15:19:43Z","name":"Esslinger Deluxe Watch Repair Tool Set","synopsis":"The Esslinger Deluxe Watch Repair Tool Set contains the tools to perform simple to more complex watch repairs. This kit works well for the beginner or experienced watchmaker.","review":{"pros":[""],"cons":[""]},"strapline":"The Esslinger Deluxe Watch Repair Tool Set contains the tools to perform simple to more complex watch repairs. This kit works well for the beginner or experienced watchmaker.","language":"en"